ing: 3/4 cup prepared fat free vanilla pudding
1 (8 ounce) container fat free frozen whipped topping, thawed
des: "This is a quick recipe for ice cream.  For mousse, freeze for four hours, then refrigerate 30 minutes before serving."
ins: Fold the pudding together with the whipped topping.   Return to whipped topping container and freeze 8 hours or overnight with lid slightly open.
